REFERRED TO CRIME VICTIMS, CRIME AND CORRECTION

Title: Repeals certain provisions of law requiring the payment of a parole supervision fee
Summary: Repeals certain provisions of law requiring the payment of a parole supervision fee.
ActClause: AN ACT to repeal subdivision 9 of section 201 of the correction law relating to the parole supervision fee
